node.text:
Mom and baby Valais Blacknose sheep! 🖤🤩

Are these the woolliest guys you've ever seen? You can find them and many more roaming the green pastures of BoPeep Valais Blacknose Farm in County Limerick.

Thanks to @bopeep_valaisblacknose for this cute shot. 👏📸
